name: Hayesfieldcat
tagline: Lucy's interactive emoji cat in Hayesfield material design colours
body:
<!DOCTYPE html>
<meta name="robots" content="noindex">
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width">
  <title>The Hayesfield Cat</title>
</head>
<body>
<svg height="600" width="600">
<!--background-->
<polygon points="0,0 600,0 600,600 0,600" fill="#F3E5F5"id= "face"/>
<!--body-->
<circle cx="300" cy="600" r="200" fill="#9575CD"/>
<circle cx="300" cy="400" r="150" fill="#00000"/>
<circle cx="300" cy="550" r= "50" fill="gold"/>
<!--ears-->
<polygon fill="#9575CD"
        points="150,50 130,200 360,200" />
<polygon fill="#9575CD"
        points="450,50 470,200 240,200" />
<polygon fill="purple"
        points="445,60 460,200 240,210" />
<polygon fill="purple"
        points="155,60 140,200 360,210" />
<!--eyes-->
<circle cx="300" cy="300" r="200" fill="#9575CD"/>
<circle cx="400" cy="240" r="20" fill="black"/>
<circle cx="200" cy="240" r="20" fill="black"/>
<circle cx="405" cy="230" r="5" fill="white"/>
<circle cx="205" cy="230" r="5" fill="white"/>
<!--L wiskers-->
<line x1="200" x2="300" y1="320" y2="320"
      stroke-width="2" stroke="#000000" stroke-linecap="round"/>
<line x1="200" x2="300" y1="350" y2="320"
      stroke-width="2" stroke="#000000" stroke-linecap="round"/>
<line x1="200" x2="300" y1="290" y2="320"
      stroke-width="2" stroke="#000000" stroke-linecap="round"/>
<!--R wiskers-->
<line x1="400" x2="300" y1="320" y2="320"
      stroke-width="2" stroke="#000000" stroke-linecap="round"/>
<line x1="400" x2="300" y1="350" y2="320"
      stroke-width="2" stroke="#000000" stroke-linecap="round"/>
<line x1="400" x2="300" y1="290" y2="320"
      stroke-width="2" stroke="#000000" stroke-linecap="round"/>
<!--mouth-->
<path fill="transparent" stroke="black" stroke-width="5" d="M 300,340 q 0,75 -75,20 " />
<path fill="transparent" stroke="black" stroke-width="5" d="M 300,340 q 0,75 75,20 " />
<!--nose-->
<polygon fill="#512DA8"
        points="300,345 275,300 330,300" />
<text x="250" y="550" fill="purple" 
    font-family="Verdana" font-size="19">
        Hayesfield
				        </text>
<text x="280" y="570" fill="purple" 
    font-family="Verdana" font-size="19">
       
				    Cat    </text>

<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.0.0.js"></script>
</svg> 
<script id="interactive-emoji">
var BackgroundShape = $("#face");
var isBackgroundBlue;
isBackgroundBlue=true

BackgroundShape.click(function() {

if(isBackgroundBlue == true){
    BackgroundShape.attr("fill", "#CE93D8");
		isBackgroundBlue = false;

  }else {
    BackgroundShape.attr("fill", "#F3E5F5");
  isBackgroundBlue = true;

}
})

</script>
</body>
</html>
